Below are some actions that will be available. Others: further crackdowns etc., reversing

- @wip1: Improve our relations with the Metropolitan Police service.
- @wip5: Recruit more officers into the Met.
- @wip6: Purge the bureaucracy of reactionary elements.
- @wip7: Introduce a state ban on the Blackshirts.
- @wip8: Introduce a state ban on the reactionary gentlemen's clubs.
- @wip9: Introduce a state ban on the communist militias.
- @wip10: Introduce a state ban on the BUF.
- @wip11: Introduce a state ban on the CPB.
- @wip12: Crack down on the reactionary media.
- @wip13: Crack down on the communist trade unions.
- @wip14: Introduce a state ban on the CUP.
- @fdf_ban: Introduce a state ban on the FDF.
- @wip2: Renegotiate our ruling coalition.
- @wip3: Renegotiate our ruling coalition.
- @wip4: Call for a snap election.

